# Commit Type Helper

- (start) Directory?
  - src/ -> feat/fix
  - tests/ -> test
  - docs/ -> docs
  - .github/ -> ci
  - scripts/ -> chore

- (type) Change?
  - Feature -> feat
  - Fix -> fix
  - Docs -> docs
  - Tests -> test
  - Tools -> chore
  - CI -> ci

- (scope) Scope? (optional)

- (desc) Description?

- Output: <type>(<scope>): <desc>
